## Practical Recommendation

> **For a work-oriented desktop, there is no strong reason to insist on PipeWire here.**

While PipeWire is a modern multimedia stack, in this setup:

- Debian *trixie* (unstable / development)
- XFCE desktop
- Typical desktop workloads (browser, office, coding)

the **stability risk outweighs the benefits**.

